---
title: South Asian-Style Jumbo Shrimp and Salmon Curry with Cilantro Rice
description: Crispy, crunchy fried shallots provide the perfect crumble for tonight's South Asian-inspired jumbo shrimp and salmon dish. Fluffy basmati rice absorbs all the velvety-smooth coconut sauce!
